::KitKat::

"We came from a cave in the forest.  Quckstrike and Stringtra were 
there.  Rowdy and I found Stringtra being held out of a pond in the 
cave, by a strange, long and skinny tentical like arm.  It let her go 
and we started snooping around.  Terrorsaur and Drillbit dug and 
found a chamber inside the cave.  A strange wolf like bot was 
standing there." She looked at the CR chamber. Maybe that's what it 
is. You see, the creature had Quickstrike held down by wires, cords 
and such.  But I have no idea what happened to him before we got 
there."  She whimpered, "I just hope he turns out OK." She layed down 
on the floor and licked her paw.  She would wait to use the CR after 
Quickstrike was out.
